{"id":28712,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/28712","type":2,"name":"アルスラーン戦記III 東の城、西の城","name_cn":"亚尔斯兰战记III 东之城 西之城","summary":"　　强盛的帕尔斯王国，因为链接东西方的大陆公路贯穿王国，故其文化和经济都非常繁盛，王都──叶克巴达那更是可以媲美东方「绢之国」首都的繁荣。但在帕尔斯历320年，帕尔斯被西方蛮族「鲁西达尼亚」入侵，本来不费吹灰之力便可获胜的帕尔斯，却因为其中一名万骑长的叛变，在平原「亚特罗帕提尼」的会战中惨败，大陆强国竟在一日之间陷入亡国的边缘。败走的帕尔斯国王安德拉寇拉斯三世，在逃亡之际被一名戴著银假面的骑士所捕。而第一次出征的王太子亚尔斯兰，在忠臣达龙的协助下从混乱的战场中死里逃生，最后到了巴休尔山找寻不被国王所重用的那尔撒斯。王太子亚尔斯兰在一智一勇的二人，以及其他投奔麾下的忠臣辅助下，踏上了艰苦的复国之路.......","eps":[{"id":136356,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/136356","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"東の城、西の城","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"1993-10-21","air_weekday":4,"rating":{"total":47,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":1,"5":4,"6":8,"7":21,"8":12,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.7},"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/02/39/28712_vwfDt.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/02/39/28712_vwfDt.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/02/39/28712_vwfDt.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/02/39/28712_vwfDt.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/02/39/28712_vwfDt.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":20,"collect":77,"doing":1,"on_hold":5,"dropped":3},"crt":[{"id":17517,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/17517","name":"アルスラーン","name_cn":"亚尔斯兰","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/1a/9d/17517_crt_3RFZB.jpg?r=1433412239","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/1a/9d/17517_crt_3RFZB.jpg?r=1433412239","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/1a/9d/17517_crt_3RFZB.jpg?r=1433412239","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1a/9d/17517_crt_3RFZB.jpg?r=1433412239"},"comment":8,"collects":21,"info":{"name_cn":"亚尔斯兰","alias":{"zh":"阿尔斯兰","en":"Arslan"},"gender":"男"},"actors":[{"id":3900,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/3900","name":"山口勝平","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/46/c8/3900_prsn_RB1me.jpg?r=1494885663","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/46/c8/3900_prsn_RB1me.jpg?r=1494885663","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/46/c8/3900_prsn_RB1me.jpg?r=1494